Reading the table:
  dated-untemplated > 0  → I add a Layer-1 template (+ completeness entry); no backfill needed.
  metadata date key      → cheap batched-UPDATE backfill from the field shown.
  srcDate% high          → backfill from the primary Source's publishedAt (per-pipeline decision).
  none of the above      → source-API sweep, or honest residue (stays curve-less).
